al\\\" style=\\\"font-size:medium;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\">You have the right to request the deletion of your personal information. We will comply with such requests unless we are required to retain the information for legal or regulatory purposes.<\\/font><\\/p><p><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-size:medium;\\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\">6.3. Consent Withdrawal<\\/font><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-size:medium;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\">If you have provided consent for the use of your personal information, you have the right to withdraw your consent at any time. This will not affect the lawfulness of processing based on consent before its withdrawal.<\\/font><\\/p><p><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-size:medium;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\"><br \\/><\\/font><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-size:medium;\\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\">7. Cookies and Tracking Technologies<\\/font><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-size:medium;\\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\">7.1. Cookies<\\/font><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-size:medium;\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\">We use cookies to enhance your experience on our platform. Cookies are small data files stored on your device that help us understand how you use our platform and improve your user experience.<\\/font><\\/p><p><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"font-size:medium;\\\"><b><font color=\\\"#000000\\\">7.2. Types of Cookies We Use<\\/font><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><ul type=\\\"disc\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-top:0cm;\\\"><li class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\"><b>Essential Cookies<\\/b>: These cookies are necessary for the operation of our platform.<\\/font><p><\\/p><\\/li><li class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><font color=\\\"#000000\\\"><b>Analytical Cookies<\\/b>: Th